attributes.Long form description: The student grabs the allen wrench to unscrew the legs. He removes the screws and places it on the table, then disassembles the first leg and puts it on the table. He turns the furniture over and unscrews the second leg,  turns the furniture and disassembles the leg, lays the furniture down and unscrews the last leg, inserts the allen wrench to unscrew and remove the first shelf. finally he removes the screws and disassembles the furniture.

attributes.Transcription: We will now disassemble the small shelf from Ikea, so please go ahead.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first leg.
The student disassembles the fourth leg.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not drop the hex socket head.
The student should not drop the hex socket head.
